metadata.name: Moon Boyz #1
metadata.description: The Moon Boyz is a collection of 11,111 unique ERC-721 tokens living on the Ethereum Blockchain. Unique and 3D designed, each NFT comes with a full membership to an ever-growing community and awesome utilities. In preparation for our trip to the moon, please find shuttle below. Single file and one at a time, keeping all hands and arms inside the spaceship until we reach our final destination. We realize you have options when it comes to space travel and we thank you for choosing Moon Boyz. Visit www.moon-boyz.com to learn more.
